BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Inside theMednet: The Community of Experts Solving Tough Clinical 
 Questions
DTSTART:20260228T000000Z
DTEND:20260228T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260309T062309Z
UID:1d80730576bf6235@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:Podcast - IDSA
DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: Let's Talk ID] Duration: 951\n\nPaul Sax\, MD\, FIDS
 A\, sits down with Patrick Passarelli\, MD\, a med-peds ID physician at Da
 rtmouth-Hitchcock and ID editor for theMednet \, to explore how clinicians
  can get expert guidance beyond AI. They dive into the origins of theMedne
 t\, what makes a great clinical question\, and how this growing community 
 of medical experts is shaping practice.\n\nEvent URL: https://www.buzzspro
 ut.com/2019912/episodes/18761120-inside-themednet-the-community-of-experts
